Sixteenth International Conference on Parallel Problem Solving from Nature (PPSN XVI)

A few more days and PPSN 2020 will start! We are looking forward very much to welcome you at the conference: on-site and on-line. A hybrid conference, combining both worlds. 99 papers, presented as posters with ample opportunities for interaction. Keynotes, tutorials, workshops, competitions.

We are very honored to have Prof. Hans-Paul Schwefel speaking in the opening session on Monday, Sep. 7!

Greetings from the organizers!

Thomas Baeck
Organizer,
Sixteenth International Conference on Parallel Problem Solving from Nature (PPSN XVI)

Late ticket registration available until the day of the conference!
https://ppsn2020.liacs.leidenuniv.nl/
